{"word":"H6884 - צָרַף - tsâraph - tsaw-raf' - Cast","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָרַף</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>tsâraph"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-raf'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cast"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - புடமிடு, பரிட்சித்துக்காட்டு, பொருந்தவை, உருக்கு, தட்டார், தட்டான், புடமிடுகிறவன், புடமிடப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to smelt, to refine, to test"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to smelt, to refine"},{"paragraph":"2) to test"},{"paragraph":"3) to test (and to prove true)"},{"paragraph":"4) a smelter, a refiner, a goldsmith (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be refined"},{"paragraph":"c) (Piel) to be arefiner; a refiner (participle)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>fuse</i> (metal), that is, <i>refine</i> (literally or figuratively): - cast, (re-) fine (-er), founder, goldsmith, melt, pure, purge away, try."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4715 - מִצְרֵף - mitsrêph - mits-rafe'/4715\">H4715</a>, <a href=\"#/H6884 - צָרַף - tsâraph - tsaw-raf'/6884\">H6884</a>, <a href=\"#/H6885 - צֹרְפִי - Tsôrᵉphîy - tso-ref-ee'/6885\">H6885</a>, <a href=\"#/H6886 - צָרְפַת - Tsârᵉphath - tsaq-ref-ath'/6886\">H6886</a>"}]}